<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph previous-next-navigation">
<p><a href="/en/markets/amazon/amazon-setup"><span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left  "></i></span> Setting up Amazon in plentymarkets</a>
<a href="/en/markets/amazon/variation-data-export">Setting up catalogues for variation export to Amazon <span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right  "></i></span></a></p>
</div>
